* Fast-Fast: Both NMOS and PMOS are fast
* Higher mobility, lower threshold voltages

* Process skew parameters (if supported by models)  
* .param NMOS_VTH_SHIFT=-0.05
* .param PMOS_VTH_SHIFT=0.05
* .param NMOS_MOBILITY_MULT=1.1
* .param PMOS_MOBILITY_MULT=1.1
